field_15_4_0.label: - Understand that if any false or deliberately misleading information is given, or any material facts withheld, I will not be accepted for employment, or if I am employed, my employment may be terminated.

field_15_5_0.label: - Authorise the examining doctor to release any information acquired from my medical history, examination and urine drug screen to authorised personnel of my prospective employer.
